## Change-Log Synopsis Entry

**US-008C — Commit-Time Allocation of SALES and PROJECT Order Numbers**  Implemented concurrency-safe commit logic for allocating immutable order numbers. SALES orders now reserve a global numeric base token using optimistic locking, while PROJECT orders derive stable base tokens from project codes and sequence only within qualifier/system contexts. Enforced canonical order number format and documented scope routing to prevent cross-scope side effects.

